Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.util

Message data container.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ByteBuffer
    Generic byte buffer, that can be used to write and read bytes from.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultByteBuffer
    Default byte buffer backed by a list of arrays to overcome the size limitations of a usual Java byte buffer.
    StreamedReadOnlyByteBuffer
    Read only byte buffer backed by an input stream.
    StreamedWriteOnlyByteBuffer
    Write only byte buffer backed by an output stream.
